title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - ATR 42-600/72-600 - now available
description:
In this video we will have a look at the ATR42-600/72-600 which has just been released to the MSFS marketplace. After going to the aircraft and livery types we will have a look at the aircraft by placing it on an airport close to Hawai and review both the exterior as well as the interior including a review of the electronic flight bag as well as the cockpit.
